videos.description: Wichita State's Markis McDuffie drives, takes on contact and makes the double pump layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: McDuffie hits acrobatic and-1

videos.description: Zach Brown intercepts a lazy pass by Ceasar DeJesus and beats a defender up the floor for a breakaway dunk.
videos.headline: UCF's Brown skies for dunk

videos.description: A.J. Davis throws down a left-handed flush after a steal and teammate Chad Brown follows with his own crowd-pleasing and-1 dunk less than a minute later.
videos.headline: Davis, Brown overpower Wichita State with emphatic dunks

videos.description: Landry Shamet reminds UCF he has hops too with an aggressive one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Wichita State's Shamet punishes rim

videos.description: Shaquille Morris makes UCF pay for not boxing him out with a huge putback dunk.
videos.headline: Morris gets up for putback dunk

videos.description: UCF's Chad Brown puts his hand up through the rim to block Darral Willis Jr.'s shot.
videos.headline: Brown denies Willis at the rim

videos.description: Shaquille Morris works for position in the paint and lays in a bucket to give Wichita State a 3-point lead late in the game.
videos.headline: Morris gets position for big bucket

videos.description: A.J. Davis drills a desperation 3-pointer with less than 10 seconds left to send UCF to overtime against Wichita State.
videos.headline: Davis' big shot sends it to overtime

videos.description: Darral Willis Jr. hits a huge step-back jumper to give Wichita State a three-point lead with less than a minute remaining.
videos.headline: Willis hits step-back jumper in overtime

videos.description: Shaquille Morris says Wichita State knew they had to "take care of business" on the road against UCF in order to compete for the AAC championship on Sunday.
videos.headline: Shaquille Morris dominates in Wichita State's overtime win
